al interesting channel divergences, such\nas the diamond norm or the Renyi channel divergence, is to determine whether,\namong all input states, a Gaussian state is optimal.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Aug 2017 02:46:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Jan 2018 18:25:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 15 Jun 2018 14:54:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-18"}
